description:
The goal of Cluster Chunk is to destroy the enemy team's bed and kill them when they cannot respawn. 

Both teams start on identical diamond shaped resource pockets, separated by the void. Each team also has the option to bridge across to 3 additional resource satellites where they can acquire extra blocks, bows/arrows, potion supplies, gunpowder, and other things.
